fields.task_description_template: Prepare and organize all learning materials, learner guides, and assessment instruments for "{qualification}". Ensure materials are ready for {learner_count} learners.

fields.name: Schedule Planning Kickoff
fields.task_description_template: Schedule and send invites for project kickoff meeting with all stakeholders for "{title}".

fields.name: Verify Venue Availability
fields.task_description_template: Verify and book venue/classroom for "{title}" delivery at {campus}. Ensure capacity for {learner_count} learners.

fields.name: Create Session Timetable
fields.task_description_template: Develop detailed session timetable and training schedule for "{qualification}". Include all modules, assessments, and workplace components.

fields.name: Notify Corporate Client
fields.task_description_template: Inform {client_name} that project "{title}" has been approved. Confirm next steps and learner nomination timeline.

fields.name: Create Cohort in System
fields.task_description_template: Set up cohort/class group in the system for "{title}". Link to qualification "{qualification}" and assign facilitator.

fields.name: Register Learners on SETA Portal
fields.task_description_template: Capture all {learner_count} learner registrations on the SETA online portal for "{title}".

fields.name: Verify Learner Documents
fields.task_description_template: Verify all learner documentation (IDs, qualifications, proof of residence) for "{title}" enrollment. Flag any outstanding items.

fields.name: Send Learner Welcome Packs
fields.task_description_template: Distribute welcome packs, learner guides, and orientation materials to all {learner_count} learners for "{title}".

fields.name: Setup Attendance Tracking
fields.task_description_template: Configure attendance tracking, registers, and QR codes for "{title}" training sessions.

fields.name: Conduct Orientation Session
fields.task_description_template: Deliver learner orientation session for "{title}". Cover program overview, expectations, assessment requirements, and support services.

fields.name: Link Learners to Host Employers
fields.task_description_template: Match and link learners to their workplace placement employers for "{title}". Ensure workplace agreements are in place.

fields.name: Submit Final Achievements to SETA
fields.task_description_template: Submit all learner achievements and results to SETA for certification. Ensure all PoE files are complete and uploaded.

fields.name: Generate Completion Report
fields.task_description_template: Compile project completion report for "{title}" including learner outcomes, pass rates, and lessons learned.

fields.name: Archive Project Documentation
fields.task_description_template: Archive all project documentation, PoE files, and learner records according to retention policy for "{title}".

fields.name: Close Out Project Finances
fields.task_description_template: Finalize all project finances for "{title}". Ensure all tranche claims are submitted and payments received.

fields.name: Collect Learner Feedback
fields.task_description_template: Distribute and collect learner feedback surveys for "{title}". Compile feedback for continuous improvement.

fields.name: Client Satisfaction Survey
fields.task_description_template: Send satisfaction survey to {client_name} regarding "{title}" delivery. Document feedback and follow-up actions.

fields.name: Confirm Stakeholder Acknowledgement
fields.task_description_template: Follow up with stakeholders who have not acknowledged their notification for "{title}". Ensure all team members are aware of their responsibilities.

fields.name: Finalize Resource Allocation
fields.task_description_template: Confirm all resource allocations and resolve any outstanding shortages for "{title}" before project start.

fields.name: Review and Approve NOT
fields.task_description_template: Review Notification of Training "{title}" for approval. Verify resource availability, budget, and stakeholder assignments.

2. PREVIOUS MINUTES
   The minutes of the previous meeting were confirmed as a true reflection.

3. TRAINING PROGRESS
   - 19 learners currently enrolled in programmes
   - 15 learners completed qualifications this quarter
   - Overall completion rate: 93%

4. BUDGET REVIEW
   - YTD spend: R613,000
   - Remaining budget: R368,000
   - On track for annual targets

5. NEW INITIATIVES
   - Proposed new skills programme for middle management
   - Digital skills training rollout planned for Q2

6. NEXT MEETING
   Scheduled for 03 December 2025
